Requirements
------------
* UNIX compatible system running X11
* GTK libraries

Installation
------------
1)  % cd washerDryer
2)  % make
3)  % make install

    Install is optional. Must be root to install.
    If any problems with make or make install, try editing the Makefile.

4)  % vi ~/.wdryerrc

    Adjust ~/.wdryerrc to your preferences.

5)  % washerDryer &
